OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA warm and
OL,6,Fsunny evening then remaining dry and
OL,7,Fclear overnight across all parts. The
OL,8,Fodd patchy of cloud will develop
OL,9,Fovernight. Light or moderate east or
OL,10,Fnortheast winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FAny early cloud will quickly
OL,13,Fclear, then another dry, sunny and
OL,14,Fvery warm day. Breezy and fresher
OL,15,Falong the County Down coast.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FA dry
OL,18,Ffew days with good spells of sunshine
OL,19,Fand remaining very warm or hot.
